reviews.review_text: The best grocery store around our home!

Its my local place and Im glad for it. Sure the prices are sometimes beat by bigger stores but they make up for that with lovely staff, well stocked shelves and a comfortable experience. Very happy with Millers YIG as my go to grocer.

Good salad area its always nice to come over get some salads to eat I love when there shelf is lots of selections, always come on Saturday to get big salad for my family . . Good talk to that lady work in salad love her work hard, I see her everywhere in the store

Thanks for supporting local - today I bought 4 jars of different craft pickles - - -thanks for perogies with no preservatives  and the dough is thin yet does  not fall apart when cooking - also very tasty - - - the organic section always has what I need - bio italia tomatoes and basilica sauce are great - - - I appreciate grass fed beef stew and ground beef and lamb

Went shopping at Miller s Sat Jan 25th in the evening. I had one of the mega packs of toilet paper on the bottom of my cart. We went to the self serve and I asked the attendant if he could please scan that item for me. He not only scanned it but scanned and bagged our entire order. Such service is above and beyond and very much appreciated. A pleasant surprise. Thank you.
The store had what I needed was nice and clean also.
Great prices small store easy to find

Nice grocery store, lots of potions, and lots of parking. I was able to order a head cakes and they had it ready for pick up. They also scan optimum points card and if you dont have the points card, get it, its worth it!

The place is fully stocked with the supplies that customers need. When going to pay, the cashiers keep the place as organized and cleaned as possible and they respect the social distancing. The products we find are very affordable, fresh and a good quality I might say. Its a good place to go for home supplies/grocery shopping. Strongly recommend.
My God, the fruits are big  ! Bought a case of strawberries and had to cut them in 4 pieces. Decent selection.

Been shopping here for 7 years and a serious points collector has saved me hundreds of  dollars on my food bill. Store is clean and well stocked. Now use in store pharmacy as we l as express shopping feature to save time via online ordering and curbside pickup. No self checkout and limited open tills can sometimes slow down the in store experience.

Has good selection, items are priced okay and fresh. Clean and spacious and the staff are nice and friendly. I havent checked if they have a restroom. Price-wise, they arent far off from other grocery stores, pretty competitive pricing. They do not have self check outs so theres usually a line up. That isnt a bad thing though.

For a large grocery store, part of loblaws they have really good customer service. They always call to confirm my PC express order and I could add items to my order if they were not online by phone. So wanted to say thank you for making my experience so much easier and smoother. They go above and beyond.
They sell all kinds of fresh bread and good ready to eat meals

This is the local grocery store closest to my home. Overall its a great store. Very clean and well organized. I do find the Independent of the Presidents Choice stores to be the most expensive. No Frills and Superstore have better prices for the same items. But they do have everything you need if you live in the area.
Excellent prices and deals

The store is a grocery store. The best part is the 50 percent off bin . Just always great things in it.  I have gotten such great items in it . Just yesterday I got my dogs food in it. Being Im injured at the moment and funds are low  these deals like this are the best.  I think there is monster drinks in the bin , like lots of them .  Also I seen vitamins in it. So Id go check out the bin of sales.  HAPPY SHOPPING   enjoy your day
a great little market hidden in the heart southeast vancouver. has virtually anything you need. no need to head down the hill to riverside district full of busy hipsters, just stop here.
Wonderful online ordering and pick up service. Very good selection and customer service. Good prices too.

Its a great place to get lunch and groceries. Everytime i come here its for lunch. You cant go wrong with a few pieces of chicken and 2 sides for $6.00 and it is good! The few times i came here they had the pork ribs but last time, they didnt. I still loved it!

I went to Miller s Your independent Grocer a month ago. The Lady in the garden was so kind and nice  .. your garden is so amazing. It s organize and clean.. I bought my healthy and beautiful cactus with a pair price..
Its a great little market for grocery shopping   never over crowded  have everything you need  and prices are reasonable

The owner actually works in this store. I can see the difference. The store is cleaner, more products are carried, fresher produce and lots of employees to serve. Prices are on par with other large supermarkets and very convenient for the area it serves. They discount near expirey meats and products.
Great place to grocery shop, clean and staff are great

Way less people to fight with as compared to metrotown superstore. Sometimes when prime rib steaks are on sale theres no stock, I need to bug them. They cut and restock it right away and all is well! Best meat for bbq when its on sale!
Great customer service Barry was very helpful very kind nice man should get a raise

A great little supermarket in the Champlain neighbourhood. Has pretty much everything you need and always good to go for last minute things youve forgotten. I like coming here because its usually a lot less busy than the superstore near my place.
Clean, attractively displayed, good Deli, Pharmacy on site. Other useful and convenient services and stores in the vicinity, including a public Library!

Keep this place open for as long as i live! Another 50! Great small uncomplicated store.  And it is not expensive since you can buy small portions. YOU VAN BUY CHEAPER AT COSTCO AND THEN YOU PUT 50% OF IT IN GREEN BIN!
The store manager her was extremely helpful in helping me locate some burgers that i could not find. He went above and beyond in ensuring exceptional customer service.
Pretty good selection of products are available . the produce section in particular is really nice . always vibrant and fresh
I was looking for a specific item. The gentleman who helped me was super, even apologizing for the lack of stock. Always a clean store.
Love the health food section where theres a much wider selection now. Would be even better if they can carry some keto bread.
Clean, nice layout. Good deals on fresh ready meals especially at 50% off some days.
The store stocks a variety of products at reasonable prices. The aisles are organized and clean. Store staff are friendly and knowledgeable.
Clean and a solid variety of goods! Plus, they have a Chinese take out, Shoe repair, Bakery with sweets (cookies and cakes), European meat store, Fido, and Lotto vender inside!
Great service and convenient
Thank God for independent.... Grocer. This place has everything we always need, emergency plunger? Dragon fruit? They got it, awesome Deli & bakery.
Prices and feel like Superstore without the maddening crowds. I would tell everyone about this place but I dont want it to get overcrowded. :)
Great store! No lines, some good prices,  good quality food.
One of my favorite stores, clean, absolutely friendly employees, plenty of candy and most of my favorite products in stock
What you want at a moments notice.  Early in the am or an evening run to the grocery of course check your store hours before going. Chances are good youll find what you .
Unbeatable Superstore Wholesale Prices. Large selection of high quality food and services at a respectable price. Highly recommended grocery location for the savvy.
Great Value, super clean environment. Lots of Fresh Soups and pre-made Foods. Amazing Deli. Fresh produce. I love this place!
Great local grocery store. The prices of Great Canadian Superstore but much smaller and less busy. Good selection all around, and good produce.
Convenient, great service, good quality, all around excellent. Staff doing a great job during these crazy times. Thank you!!!
Great place to shop. Deli has a wide variety of items,  and there are lots of sales throughout the store.
Great team, reasonable prices for a smaller store, excellent pharmacy team as well
The Best  Mall in BC. Starbucks is the same but woearkerss  make difference,  friendly nice  people
Go there once a day. Small but great selection. Easy to go in and out. M
Place was nice and tidy. The quality of the produce was great. Decent amount of choices.
Please note that Pharmacy hours are different from store hours pharmacy is open Monday to Friday 9am-9pm Saturday 9am-6pm and Sunday 10am-6pm
Really friendly staff. They dont have been sprouts there though but basically everything else
Better prices than Safeway
Decent grocery store nothing to write home about
Theyve just renewed and it looks great. It looks like they might start the pick up grocery option soon too.
Good prices good choices always plus really friendly staff
i love this place. its not big and not small. the clerks always have a few minutes to chat with you.
Clean, friendly staff & good prices.
Love the store! Has everything that is needed at the basic level
Great customer service here. Especially Roma!!!
Close to my home. My favorite place.
I have an odd work schedule so I love that theyre open until 3 am.
My neighbour grocery store! Always nice shopping experience.
Went through Jose s line and he was hilarious. Definitely made a boring grocery shop into a fun time
Great place for a quick shop or a large order. They got everything!
Easy to park.reasonable price,convenient. Accessible to the bus stop.
My regular store. Over it. But one particular staff is quite rude.
Its a good store .got what I needed
Beautiful selection of orchard grown Apples :) Macintosh was excellent!!
Good for shoppers
Great prices o.k selection
great staff really like the store very clean also
My fave grocery store always have what I am looking for.
Love it Big tome
Great food and great services and the name says It all in very helpful
Great Shop
Great local grocery. Has the essentials a superstore would have.
Very nice place to work.
Good place to go with fake girls
One stop shopping quick and friendly staff at your service.
Good value and nice portions of meat and veggies
Great people working there. I go there all the time.
Great selection of groceries. Friendly staff.
Pleasant place to shop. Interesting food court.
Good place to get all ur grocery shopping done in one place
Great place to buy food, inexpensive and great service
Fair prices, good inventory
Super staff lots of inventory. Convenient and lots of parking.
Great place only place I go since covid started
Groceries are right here !! And yes they are hiring for cashiers atm!
U can get all ur grocery shopping done here
Great staff.  Great selection of food.
Very nice and convenient
Good customer service - professional and kind.
Fine,  got what I wanted.  Everything looked good
Any other place doesnt look like this is certainly amazing!
Great Selection.  Friendly staff.  Friendly patrons.
Very good stock.
Good store. Lots of variety
